OL,3,CFormer firefighter handed community
OL,4,Corder for racially aggravated
OL,5,Charassment
OL,7,FA former firefighter who admitted to
OL,8,Fracially aggravated harassment of a
OL,9,FBlack colleague has avoided jail.
OL,11,FStephen Suggitt, of Brook Lane in
OL,12,FWhitby, was a watch manager based at
OL,13,FThornaby Fire Station, where he led
OL,14,FCleveland Fire Brigade's 'Green Unit'.
OL,16,FSuggitt subjected a black colleague
OL,17,Fwho was under his command to racial
OL,18,Fslurs in messages posted in a Whatsapp
OL,19,Fgroup.
