OL,4,Corder for racially aggravated
OL,5,Charassment
OL,7,FAt an earlier hearing at Teesside
OL,8,FCrown Court, the jury heard that
OL,9,FSuggitt had nicknamed the victim
OL,10,F'Harvey' in reference to the celebrity
OL,11,FKatie Price's mixed race son, who has
OL,12,Fa number of medical and learning
OL,13,Fdifficulties.
OL,15,FThe prosecution said Suggitt's
OL,16,Fbehaviour had "crossed a line from
OL,17,Fharmless banter".
