OL,7,FHe spoke outside court to apologise
OL,8,Ffor his actions.
OL,10,FSuggitt resigned from the service
OL,11,Fafter an investigation was launched
OL,12,Finto his behaviour.
OL,14,FIn a statement Cleveland Fire Brigade
OL,15,Fsaid they do not comment on individual
OL,16,Fcases, but added: "We take any form of
OL,17,Fdiscrimination, harassment, or
OL,18,Foffensive behaviour extremely
OL,19,Fseriously.
